<template>
  {{fontFile.MainMenu}}
</template>

<script>
import bus from '@/util/Bus'
export default {
  name: "Main_menu",
  data(){
    return{
      fontFile:""
    }
  },
  Create() {
    bus.on("getFontFile",(val)=>{
      this.fontFile = val
    })
  },
  mounted() {
    console.log(this.fontFile)
  }
}
</script>

<style lang="less" scoped>
@import "../../less/main";

</style>
